response.overview: Watch some of wrestling fan's favorite match-ups with this great collection brought to you by the World Wrestling Federation and Coliseum Home Video. See the Undertaker team up with the Legion Of Doom to take on the Beverly Brothers & the Mountie. Also Randy Savage battles the Berzerker, Earthquake brawls with the Ultimate Warrior, Bret "Hitman" Hart goes up against Skinner, and the Nasty Boys take on the Natural Disasters.
response.title: Wrestling's Fan Favorite Matches
